l." Nephrol Dial Transplant 26 (2011): 1615-21[5] "Product Information. Rocaltrol (calcitriol)." Roche Laboratories, Nutley, NJ.[6] "Product Information. Xatral (alfuzosin)." Sanofi-Synthelabo Canada Inc, Markham, ON.[7] "Product Information. Renagel (sevelamer)." Genzyme Corporation, Cambridge, MA.', 1767369485);
